{"tid":212804,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"求救，有無人試過生唇瘡？","createTime":"2017-04-22T17:07:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-03T02:07:39.000Z","uid":100645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5fd4c463a6849cd97e432b4d98a384c876f7dc89","tid":212804,"uid":100645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T17:07:42.000Z","msg":"有無人生過唇瘡分享下？我生左好幾日了，搽藥膏好似剌痛咁，無咩用，同時間我又生緊飛之，真係痛到喊，有無人有方法？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72df4619723d76b81b04600b82d39aa18c313018","tid":212804,"uid":16685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T17:09:25.000Z","msg":"兩日無事啦喎，琴日先斷尾"},{"pid":"78fb3a6b0bd4c664bdd36a138cf6af5592102796","tid":212804,"uid":72173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T17:09:41.000Z","msg":"你係一粒過定係一點點白色果種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上年有次生，生左成個幾星期先退哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成個星期唔想見人"},{"pid":"e95b19ff1df82dcdcaa12d7812c2dd1eb94fde0f","tid":212804,"uid":100645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T17:11:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係一粒過定係一點點白色果種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上年有次生，生左成個幾星期先退哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成個星期唔想見人</blockquote><br />\n唇瘡就2粒，一粒以為普通粉刺，格硬整爆佢先發覺係唇瘡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b22b715447d1207c4e4cc3ba149f80049775043","tid":212804,"uid":100645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T17:12:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兩日無事啦喎，琴日先斷尾</blockquote><br />\n飛之定唇瘡？我2樣一齊生緊,都成個禮拜，有咩方法？"},{"pid":"513c17141619369531c58a1b2eda6d9c7fc23253","tid":212804,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T17:14:05.000Z","msg":"正常一星期就消晒"},{"pid":"d5c1780d94d0f9efa2bbeb5162d0c483f39a4954","tid":212804,"uid":16685,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T17:16:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>兩日無事啦喎，琴日先斷尾</blockquote><br />\n飛之定唇瘡？我2樣一齊生緊,都成個禮拜，有咩方法？</blockquote><br />\n熱氣姐其實，我都唔知點解咁快好，果晚飲完酒第二日就好番，我生唇瘡"},{"pid":"9a5d2e93fcd1b94b92e56e1f80cd19ea50f93038","tid":212804,"uid":100645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T17:16:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正常一星期就消晒</blockquote><br />\n我真係成個禮拜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34b0e2132c3395ec30e032323155eb33ad0a4039","tid":212804,"uid":7119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T17:17:32.000Z","msg":"可能細菌感染"},{"pid":"8d03becd0809375de78621860b77c483177df1dc","tid":212804,"uid":5480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T17:18:36.000Z","msg":"好似話係抵抗力低先會生 上網睇<br />\n試過病緊連續生三粒 兩個禮拜先好返哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ecae588653b127b01dc93d8472ddb5078a7c20d","tid":212804,"uid":100645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T17:19:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似話係抵抗力低先會生 上網睇<br />\n試過病緊連續生三粒 兩個禮拜先好返哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我長期病緊"},{"pid":"026c14b3285e843f72a412ae4f989f719deab4d2","tid":212804,"uid":39132,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T17:20:02.000Z","msg":"唇瘡唔是hpv咩<br />\n冇得斷尾跟一世<br />\n只係發唔發出黎咁解"},{"pid":"8065c4ac588928743f5fab4fe4cf1e91d512fc64","tid":212804,"uid":28574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T17:26:35.000Z","msg":"我呢排都有唇瘡，keep住爆下唔爆下都有成2個月"},{"pid":"255b057d9af30565f9ec3907a0cd787d48bc53b3","tid":212804,"uid":107189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T17:27:51.000Z","msg":"去藥房配支唇瘡膏 ，keep住係咁茶！如果怕樣衰就帶口罩，不過記得要keep dry! 唔好lam佢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大約一星期會好。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f03b6c4358b75fcc36a32e9e49f3e9b6048e0f82","tid":212804,"uid":100645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T17:31:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去藥房配支唇瘡膏 ，keep住係咁茶！如果怕樣衰就帶口罩，不過記得要keep dry! 唔好lam佢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大約一星期會好。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係覺得搽完好痛，更加傷咁！翻工帶唔到口罩"},{"pid":"f64e8a7a64c947950efd9492192fa91727f47038","tid":212804,"uid":24910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T17:33:03.000Z","msg":"轉天氣好大機會出...依家醒左 一feel 到嘴角㷫㷫地就搽藥膏禁住去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為出左又要等成個星期先好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89523c5facab65bf4e773e995d877e8bca4643a4","tid":212804,"uid":24910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T17:34:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去藥房配支唇瘡膏 ，keep住係咁茶！如果怕樣衰就帶口罩，不過記得要keep dry! 唔好lam佢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大約一星期會好。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係覺得搽完好痛，更加傷咁！翻工帶唔到口罩</blockquote><br />\n會痛嫁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你係咪搞損左"},{"pid":"702b81f6cfcac03ef87262435e89bc979be75a35","tid":212804,"uid":107189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T17:44:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去藥房配支唇瘡膏 ，keep住係咁茶！如果怕樣衰就帶口罩，不過記得要keep dry! 唔好lam佢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大約一星期會好。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係覺得搽完好痛，更加傷咁！翻工帶唔到口罩</blockquote><br />\n如果出水/血就印乾佢，見佢漲到就核爆就忍忍痛擠一擠啲血水出黎，層皮甩就用夾慢慢撕走佢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n痛係正常，因為係過濾性病毒，傷口會姆姆地！<br />\n<br />\n利申，由細到大虧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，生左幾廿年"},{"pid":"97864ed799a026cb80c72713663244397fcd5473","tid":212804,"uid":81609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T18:15:41.000Z","msg":"唇瘡應該係病毒感染，個人免疫力一低就會中架喇，可以試下搽Acyclovir<br />\n<br />\n唔急既話佢2個星期左右會自己好的，不過個印都有機會留2個月左右<br />\n<br />\n利申: 有讀過下書"},{"pid":"c3f13dabcc6357c83e009550335228e9d9341cd4","tid":212804,"uid":26084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T19:27:19.000Z","msg":"唇瘡即係泡疹"},{"pid":"607b4bd493cbe1d080834b41cb9d93806c9703df","tid":212804,"uid":76038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T19:29:40.000Z","msg":"每年都會生 兩個禮拜冇野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdbd4f6fb1fb9579ef95cd1aee19d55d4c3458c5","tid":212804,"uid":100645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T22:09:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去藥房配支唇瘡膏 ，keep住係咁茶！如果怕樣衰就帶口罩，不過記得要keep dry! 唔好lam佢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大約一星期會好。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係覺得搽完好痛，更加傷咁！翻工帶唔到口罩</blockquote><br />\n如果出水/血就印乾佢，見佢漲到就核爆就忍忍痛擠一擠啲血水出黎，層皮甩就用夾慢慢撕走佢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n痛係正常，因為係過濾性病毒，傷口會姆姆地！<br />\n<br />\n利申，由細到大虧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，生左幾廿年</blockquote><br />\n每日都痛醒"},{"pid":"42ec51d1c62328210e70c1000459a0bc81f9c3b8","tid":212804,"uid":13700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T22:21:42.000Z","msg":"我生親都一定含龍，跟住攞支棉花棒濕啲漱口水去刮爆粒瘡，連龍帶血整走哂岀黎，呢個步驟痛到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好彩嘅就會結焦然後幾日好返，唔好彩嘅就可能要刮多一兩次先清哂啲龍先好返<br />\n<br />\n生過3,4次"},{"pid":"58e51dc46e0bcc5753240d9058086b8a19217bd6","tid":212804,"uid":28574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T02:31:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2o0N36h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2o0N36h.jpg&h=7b73042a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我呢種係咪唇瘡？<br />\n<br />\n時有時無，買左唇瘡膏 唔見好似你地話會痛<br />\n呢粒野 得閒腫下 1星期後又平翻 之後又腫過<br />\n呢種情況keep左2個月<br />\n有無人救我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adb6de32a7ac7d52dd5791e44b4928fd826e694a","tid":212804,"uid":100645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T02:36:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2o0N36h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2o0N36h.jpg&h=7b73042a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我呢種係咪唇瘡？<br />\n<br />\n時有時無，買左唇瘡膏 唔見好似你地話會痛<br />\n呢粒野 得閒腫下 1星期後又平翻 之後又腫過<br />\n呢種情況keep左2個月<br />\n有無人救我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係飛之來咩"}]}